formulas, incorporating terms which disappear in the infinite-energy limit.\nUsing these methods, the calculation can be adapted to produce reasonable\nresults at high transverse momentum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 19:43:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-30"}
