ts give strong evidence for the\nconjecture that the thermal deconfining transition is governed by a universal\nmechanism, common to all simple gauge groups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 20:01:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2015 20:50:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-16"}
