ust over a wide range of tau occupancies than the\ndynamic instability. We suggest in vitro tests of our predicted collapse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 20:49:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-01"}
