hanges. With workloads based on the real-world topologies, T-Cache detects\n43-70% of the inconsistencies and increases the rate of consistent transactions\nby 33-58%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 20:53:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2015 13:25:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 26 Apr 2015 19:28:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
