er of hours. Using our formulation,\nstudying scientifically-relevant problems is a computationally reasonable task.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 22:17:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Apr 2015 00:43:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-11"}
