 universal process, i.e. the direct\noutcome of gravitationally unstable fluctuations in a density field initially\ngenerated by large scale shock-dominated turbulence. This globally enables us\nto infer the variations of the stellar IMF and related properties for atypical\ngalactic conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Sep 2014 10:30:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
