re. The evaluation of circular polarisation is challenging; a\nnumber of one-photon experiments of 1E9 or more is needed to resolve\nhemispherically-integrated degrees of circular polarisation of a few times\n1E-5. Last, I introduce brightness curves...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Sep 2014 14:52:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
