valence principles including the\nuniversality of the gravitational redshift and the free fall and law of\nreciprocal action and on the kinetic energy of composite system. The concern\nabout the compatibility with the equivalence principles, the universality of\ngravitational redshift and the free fall and law of reciprocal action should be\naddressed. We conclude that the value of the GUP parameters remain a puzzle to\nbe verified.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 22:59:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Nov 2014 18:31:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-24"}
