ion of the inflaton field to the energy-momentum\ntensor is negligible compared to the contribution of the radiation fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Sep 2014 22:12:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-08"}
